<p style="margin-bottom: 8px; text-indent: 0em; line-height: 2em;"><span style="line-height: 115%; font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;">亲爱的朋友，你好！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px;">我是中国电商视觉标准第一人——朱华杰（花名：弥乐），专注电商视觉营销18余载，</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px; line-height: 18.4px; color: red;">独创了一套电商视觉标准体系</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 32px;">，帮助无数电商老板摆脱了视觉困境！</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;"><span style="text-indent: 2em; font-size: 16px;">也许，你还在为视觉的事懊恼不已：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;">为什么就</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; color: red;">招不到一个好美工</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;">？</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;">为什么店铺</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; color: red;">转化率一直低</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;">行业水平？</span></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;">为什么美工做出来的</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px; color: red;">图片没有品牌感</span><span style="font-family: &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, sans-serif; text-indent: 28px;">，只能靠打价格战苦苦支撑？</span></span></p><p style="margin-bottom: 3px; te